headline: Artisan Global Discovery Fund Sold GoDaddy (GDDY) Due to Increased Competition
summary: Artisan Partners, an investment management company, released its “Artisan Global Discovery Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the second quarter, the fund’s Investor Class APFDX returned 10.84%, Advisor Class APDDX posted a return of 10.83%, and Institutional Class APHDX returned 10.93%, compared to a 11.84% return […]

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Find Risky
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
